videos.description: Oklahoma State's Phil Forte III steals a pass then on the other end lays it in.
videos.headline: Forte III  darts for the steal and lay-in for the Cowboys

videos.description: Iowa State's Matt Thomas bounces a pass to Darrell Bowie who throws down a dunk with two hands.
videos.headline: Bowie dunks off of great Thomas pass for Iowa State

videos.description: Iowa State's Monte Morris tips in a shot as chaos ensues around him with players on both sides falling to the floor.
videos.headline: Morris scores for the Cyclones as bodies fly to the floor

videos.description: Iowa State head coach Steve Prohm on what his team needs to do better on the defensive side in the second half.
videos.headline: Prohm on his team's defense in the first half

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Jawun Evans cuts into the lane then perfectly places a floater over a defender for the score.
videos.headline: Evans drops floater over an outstretched hand for Oklahoma State

videos.description: Iowa State's Deonte Burton misses a huge dunk, but is able to score and draw a foul after the miss.
videos.headline: Burton misses monster dunk but keeps focus and scores plus the foul

videos.description: Iowa State's Monte Morris whips a pass to Darrell Bowie, who slams it over an Oklahoma State defender.
videos.headline: Great pass sets up an even better slam for Iowa State

videos.description: Iowa State's Monte Morris talks about who he would like to see in the next round of the tournament.
videos.headline: Morris: "A Kansas Iowa State  matchup would be fun"
